data.description: Very well-maintained home, located just outside the city limits of Madill on 1.3 acres!  Property includes a 30x24 insulated shop, new storm cellar, shed, storage building, generator & so much more!  This beautiful home is also being offered with all appliances & some furniture.  Beautiful white fencing in the front, along with paved driveway, add to the beauty of this home!  Call soon on this one!
